    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-12-10T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-12-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="1458"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1458">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.52/480.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to Consul
                            <persName type="to">Canada</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-12-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 10, 1914</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Request Carranza to inform you immediately reason for execution Spanish subjects
                    Vidal and Sabugal, inviting his attention to facts reported by Bevan that chief
                    military official, Tampico, ignorant of reason and Governor Caballero failed to
                    reply to Bevan’s request for information, although latter is in charge Spanish
                    interests. Ask Carranza to give immediate orders that no summary measures be
                    taken against remaining Spanish prisoner Zorilla.</p>
                <p>Advise Bevan these instructions and that Department directs him to insist that
                    local authorities take no summary measures against Zorilla.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Bryan</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
